# speedcap — optional vehicle top-speed limiter (empty by default).
#
# Filled in at build time when VAN85 is set (see ci/build-map.sh): it caps the
# routing road-speed class so the router never assumes a speed above the
# vehicle's real maximum. Only LOWERS fast/unlimited roads (Autobahn, 100+);
# roads already posted below the cap keep their (lower) speed.
#
# Class -> tier in inc/roadspeed:  4 = <=85 km/h, 5 = <=100 km/h.
# Leave empty for a normal (uncapped) map.
